# ── WordWheel — Netlify _redirects ────────────────────────
#
# Format: from  to  [status]
# Docs:   https://docs.netlify.com/routing/redirects/

# Redirect bare domain to index (belt-and-suspenders; Netlify
# serves index.html by default but this makes it explicit)
/           /index.html   200

# Splat fallback — any unknown path serves the app shell so
# a user sharing a direct URL still lands on the game rather
# than a 404.  Use 200 (rewrite) not 301 so the URL is kept.
/*          /index.html   200
